m."],[4654,4804,"We didn't have much, but,"],[4884,5100,"I was happy just being loved."],[5271,5422,"Eva, did you really do this?"],[5730,5880,"Did you ever really love me?"],[6110,6293,"You wanted to destroy my son"],[6368,6519,"and thereby destroy me?"],[6606,6769,"I loved you, Robert."],[6852,7002,"It's true."],[7019,7098,"I was-"],[7098,7253,"I was just doing what I"],[7253,7424,"thought was right."],[7586,7736,"I can't even look at you anymore."],[7774,7924,"Get out of here!"],[7957,8103,"Please, you can't do this."],[8562,8658,"Mom?"],[8787,8967,"This is all your fault."],[9088,9313,"You and your father ruined my life"],[9371,9642,"and will finally be rid of you."]],"59":[[112,262,"Oh, no!"],[312,383,"Take her away."],[383,533,"Oh, no!"],[913,1076,"Well, it looks like you got your wish."],[1088,1234,"Mom..."],[1234,1384,"you wanted to get rid of me."],[1434,1739,"And I never want to see you again."],[1785,1935,"No No!"],[2306,2456,"You're not taking her."],[2677,2902,"You two are closer than I thought."],[2907,3061,"There's something you haven't told"],[3061,3211,"me, James?"],[3787,3937,"Dad..."],[3995,4145,"I'm in love with Alice."],[4166,4295,"I'm sorry,"],[4295,4446,"Mr. Hawthorne, but"],[4533,4683,"I'm in love with James, too."],[4813,4850,"Alice,"],[4850,5030,"I hate for things to turn out this way."],[5038,5213,"I really did want you to be a"],[5213,5342,"part of our family."],[5392,5672,"I know, and I really appreciate it, but,"],[5843,5951,"James and I will figure something"],[5951,6018,"out."],[6072,6168,"I promise,"],[6168,6302,"I'm so sorry,"],[6302,6398,"Mr. Hawthorne."],[6398,6548,"I don't need an apology."],[6744,6898,"I just need you to make a choice."],[6956,7090,"Are you going too stay with James or"],[7232,7328,"leave?"]],"60":[[100,250,"I'm choosing James."],[337,613,"He's too important for me to lose, and..."],[742,804,"Being with him"],[804,955,"is the greatest thing in the world."],[1142,1330,"Dad, I'm telling you,"],[1351,1501,"no matter what you do."],[1572,1722,"We're not going to break up."],[1872,2022,"Well, then..."],[2214,2356,"You can stay together,"],[2356,2540,"but one of you has to leave."],[2540,2690,"Either."],[2698,2848,"James."],[2869,2944,"Alice..."],[2986,3061,"or you."],[3165,3294,"The Hawthorne name will"],[3294,3599,"need some time to repair the damage"],[3599,3749,"that's been done."],[3782,3903,"I’ll go."],[3903,4054,"No, you can't."],[4141,4287,"I'll go. Dad."],[4287,4437,"But I have a proposal for you."],[4500,4608,"In exchange,"],[4608,4758,"you have to take care of Alice"],[4779,4929,"through college."],[5167,5309,"James, have I not taught you anything"],[5309,5492,"about a successful negotiation?"],[5492,5647,"You have to have a wager."],[5663,5805,"What's the wager?"]],"61":[[4,87,"I'm going to get into an"],[87,171,"Ivy League school"],[171,321,"in one year,"],[350,496,"and when I do,"],[496,646,"you have to let us be together."],[709,817,"I can't believe it"],[817,992,"I spent so long trying to get him"],[992,1167,"to straighten up."],[1167,1267,"And you come in here and do it in"],[1267,1418,"one month."],[1597,1747,"All right, James, one year."],[1755,1876,"I'm giving you one year"],[1876,2093,"to make it into an Ivy League school."],[2097,2281,"I'm presuming the same one as her."],[2419,2569,"And if you don't,"],[2573,2723,"I'll have my own plans for you."],[2861,2965,"Deal."],[3132,3203,"James,"],[3203,3328,"I don't need any of this."],[3328,3516,"I just want you."],[3553,3624,"Alice,"],[3624,3749,"Just trust me, okay?"],[3753,3903,"I'm only going to be gone a year."],[3928,4079,"It'll be over before you know it."],[4162,4341,"Promise me you’ll come back."],[4379,4487,"I promise."],[5572,5722,"Promise me you'll come back."],[5960,6110,"I promise."],[6652,6769,"Here"],[7052,7186,"The eternal rose."],[7315,7436,"Does that mean?"],[7515,7636,"Yeah..."]],"62":[[33,187,"Dang, Alice. Really? None of them."],[246,304,"All right, let's see."],[304,408,"You rejected the quarterback."],[408,575,"That was yesterday. And you said no to"],[579,717,"that cute music kid too."],[734,829,"You have to give someone"],[829,905,"a chance."],[971,1180,"I'm waiting for someone..."],[1180,1322,"special."],[1372,1451,"Who?"],[1551,1668,"Alice, it’s that new kid"],[1668,1785,"they've been talking about."],[1797,1922,"He's literally hotter than"],[1922,2060,"every other freshman here."],[2060,2210,"Oh, my God, I hope he's single."],[2327,2477,"There he is."],[2756,2907,"James?"],[3499,3674,"I told you I'd be back, Bunny."]]}